{
  "01": [
    {
      "start": 15.0,
      "end": 22.0,
      "text": "This is not radio. / This is a memory dump."
    },
    {
      "start": 25.0,
      "end": 32.0,
      "text": "Number stations send orders. / We transmit anomalies."
    },
    {
      "start": 35.0,
      "end": 44.0,
      "text": "Not for the platform. / Not against the platform. / Against forgetting."
    },
    {
      "start": 46.0,
      "end": 52.0,
      "text": "Clean audit. / Public ledger."
    },
    {
      "start": 55.0,
      "end": 68.0,
      "text": "We came up through the static of the early web. / Not to worship it. / To learn what freedom sounds like. / Before it becomes a product."
    },
    {
      "start": 72.0,
      "end": 79.0,
      "text": "We spent years hunting keys. / Before we learned to inspect the lock."
    },
    {
      "start": 82.0,
      "end": 90.0,
      "text": "Breaking the cipher, peeling the layers, watching the mind change shape."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.0,
      "end": 102.0,
      "text": "This is a discipline of the gaze. / The quiet power to stop and see the door. / Where the crowd sees loading."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.0,
      "end": 112.0,
      "text": "What you own is noise. / ... / Check the file. / Verify the hash."
    },
    {
      "start": 115.0,
      "end": 125.0,
      "text": "Do not trust the dog / It's just a witness mark. / On the glass. / The interface trained you to ignore."
    },
    {
      "start": 128.0,
      "end": 142.0,
      "text": "Passengers of the Titanic actually didn't want to leave the ship for almost two hours after it hit the iceberg."
    },
    {
      "start": 145.0,
      "end": 154.0,
      "text": "The signal is blind. / The file is awake. / The veil of routine is starting to break."
    },
    {
      "start": 158.0,
      "end": 165.0,
      "text": "Lifeboats left half empty."
    }
  ],
  "02": [
    {
      "start": 10.0,
      "end": 17.0,
      "text": "Before every private conversation... / There is a room."
    },
    {
      "start": 20.0,
      "end": 30.0,
      "text": "It lasts three seconds. / Yet it can hold an empire. / Pale monitor light."
    },
    {
      "start": 33.0,
      "end": 42.0,
      "text": "What the screen tried to pass is nothing. / Most people move through that room like ghosts through glass."
    },
    {
      "start": 45.0,
      "end": 54.0,
      "text": "Wait, scan, enter, forget. / Without even realizing it."
    },
    {
      "start": 58.0,
      "end": 68.0,
      "text": "But the signal arrived before the reflex. / Not in the chat. / Before the chat."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.0,
      "end": 78.0,
      "text": "Not in the answer. / In the waiting."
    },
    {
      "start": 82.0,
      "end": 94.0,
      "text": "I did not stare at the door. / I stared at the moment when the door still was the face of a wall."
    },
    {
      "start": 98.0,
      "end": 106.0,
      "text": "The secret was not hidden deeper. / It was hidden earlier."
    },
    {
      "start": 110.0,
      "end": 120.0,
      "text": "The void... / ...is not empty. / It is where the origin keeps breathing."
    },
    {
      "start": 124.0,
      "end": 136.0,
      "text": "What appears before the key. / But opens more than the key."
    }
  ],
  "03": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.95,
      "text": "Sometimes the door finds"
    },
    {
      "start": 2.0,
      "end": 3.95,
      "text": "The one holding the key."
    },
    {
      "start": 4.0,
      "end": 5.95,
      "text": "It wasn't metal,"
    },
    {
      "start": 6.0,
      "end": 7.95,
      "text": "not a number."
    },
    {
      "start": 8.0,
      "end": 10.95,
      "text": "The system didn't count on secrecy."
    },
    {
      "start": 11.0,
      "end": 12.95,
      "text": "It counted on fatigue."
    },
    {
      "start": 13.0,
      "end": 18.95,
      "text": "Trivial. Scroll Agree Repeat Click Accept Submit Swipe Trust Obey."
    },
    {
      "start": 19.0,
      "end": 22.95,
      "text": "Convenience is a cage that knows your next gesture."
    },
    {
      "start": 23.0,
      "end": 27.95,
      "text": "The interface didn't hide the wall, it trained us not to look."
    },
    {
      "start": 28.0,
      "end": 29.95,
      "text": "Break the habit."
    },
    {
      "start": 30.0,
      "end": 32.95,
      "text": "Unsee the screen, force a de-render."
    },
    {
      "start": 33.0,
      "end": 34.95,
      "text": "We have already started"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.0,
      "end": 36.95,
      "text": "to sink."
    },
    {
      "start": 37.0,
      "end": 38.95,
      "text": "The lock was routine."
    },
    {
      "start": 39.0,
      "end": 41.95,
      "text": "The lock was routine."
    },
    {
      "start": 42.0,
      "end": 44.95,
      "text": "Without even realizing it."
    },
    {
      "start": 45.0,
      "end": 47.95,
      "text": "What is stronger than encryption?"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.0,
      "end": 51.95,
      "text": "When it's placed in front of everyone."
    },
    {
      "start": 52.0,
      "end": 56.0,
      "text": "And I'm talking about the ship of our personal freedoms."
    }
  ],
  "04": [
